Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:43.97,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}nageku mamonaku toki wa nagareru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.34,0:22:44.02,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}I keď si vzdychneš, čas poletí ďalej,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.97,0:22:48.27,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}hitoritachi tomaru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:48.54,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}ale zastaví sa pre tých, čo ostali sami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:55.69,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}yume mamoru shirabe kuchizusamu no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:55.81,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Nôtim si melódiu, čo chráni naše sny,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:23:00.03,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}hitobito ga nemuri ni tsukeba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.24,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}aby každý mohol zaspať sám.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:02.91,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}mata au hi no
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:02.91,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Spať, túžiac znova sa stretnúť
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:08.08,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}negai tsumugeru deshou ai no ito
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.91,0:23:08.08,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}a zamotať sa do vlákien lásky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:11.00,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}yasashisa wo sasoru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:11.00,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}Dobro zvíťazí tak,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:18.25,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}otogibanashi anata kara osowatta no yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.00,0:23:18.50,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}ako v rozprávkach, o ktorých si mi rozprával.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:21.80,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}odorimashou sotto
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:28.39,Lyrics_B_SK,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}Tak odtancujme spolu do našich spomienok.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.97,0:23:28.22,Lyrics_B_JAP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,350)}ano koro no omoi ni
